[I] Library for reading and writing Jcat files

[T] libjcat allows reading and writing gzip-compressed JSON catalog files,
[T] which can be used to store GPG, PKCS-7 and SHA-256 checksums for each file.

[U] https://github.com/hughsie/libjcat

[A] Richard Hughes
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/development
[F] CROSS

